Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:06.75,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}your wandering shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.25,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}I could never tell you all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:16.18,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,250)}It was so very frustrating.
